      "span_text": "Assemblies, annotations, and all assembly summary statistics were computed in under an hour, using approximately 40 gigabytes (GB) of RAM. Consistent with previous findings [CITATION_1] ) the CISA integrated contigs produced superior assemblies in terms of N50, contig length, and number of contigs in nearly all samples (see Table 1 ).",
